            <qualityControl>
                <description>
                    <para>The authors of publications are fully responsible for the quality of data provided within the dataset. We used GBIF Backbone Taxonomy (GBIF species matching tool: https://www.gbif.org/tools/species-lookup) for the taxonomic check and implemented minor corrections of species names regarding misprints and problematic taxa to avoid misinterpretation. The data were first checked and verified manually using MS Excel and then additionally cross-checked in the OpenRefine environment. GBIF data validator has been applied to final check the dataset before uploading. We additionally checked and verified the header data  and QGIS 3.22 (https://qgis.org) for quality control.</para>
                </description>
            </qualityControl>
